<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/124983-who-else-was-annoyed-by-the-writing-tho">who else was annoyed by the writing? (tho, creachers etc.)</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_124983'><a id="like_count_community_question_124983" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/124983?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">70 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20758104-the-knife-of-never-letting-go">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/124983-who-else-was-annoyed-by-the-writing-tho">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/124983-who-else-was-annoyed-by-the-writing-tho">See all 44 answers</a>
</li>
