<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You know he&apos;s a good villain when you don&apos;t even see him for half this series, yet you feel hate and anger towards him. haha. And him being a corrupt <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You know he's a good villain when you don't even see him for half this series, yet you feel hate and anger towards him. haha. And him being a corrupt politician hits too close to home lol. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
