              <span id="reviewTextContainer37003748" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10738798809230191985">Hard to know how to rate this book. It is amazing and powerful, but so sad it made me angry and made me not want to recommend it to anyone. If you&apos;re up for a punch in the stomach. . . here&apos;s your book.</span>
  <span id="freeText10738798809230191985" style="display:none">Hard to know how to rate this book. It is amazing and powerful, but so sad it made me angry and made me not want to recommend it to anyone. If you're up for a punch in the stomach. . . here's your book.</span>
